      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but isn't it also true that some media outlets actually do manufacture news or lean so hard into one side that it basically becomes fake? like, shouldn't we be just as critical of \"partisan media\" as we are of politicians using the label? it feels like everyone's accusing everyone else of being fake news without actually looking at the facts.",
